visual.name: 3D Pie Chart by iFour
visual.description: A Custom Pie Chart is a type of chart that visually represents parts of a whole, with each slice showing a category's proportion. Labels and lines help identify each slice, and the chart adjusts responsively to fit the display area and avoid label overlap, making it easy to compare categories at a glance.
